 Fatboy Slim 为国家专辑日发行 25 周年纪念版《宝贝，你已经走过了很长一段路》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-releases-25th-anniversary-reissue-of-youve-come-a-long-way-baby-for-national-album-day-3515045？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fatboy-slim-releases-25th-anniversary-reissue-of-youve-come-a-long-way-baby-for-national-album-dayEmma Wilkes Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:55:54 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3515045 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="胖男孩苗条" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>制片人表示：“我仍然对《宝贝，你已经走了很长一段路》的反应感到惊讶和高兴。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-releases-25th-anniversary-reissue-of-youve-come-a-long-way-baby-for-national-album-day-3515045">Fatboy Slim 为全国专辑日发行 25 周年纪念再版《You&#39;ve Come A Long Way, Baby》，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="胖男孩苗条" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-mat-hayward-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatboy-slim">Fatboy Slim</a>今天（10 月 14 日）发行了他的开创性专辑《You&#39;ve Come A Long Way, Baby》的 25 周年纪念再版，以庆祝国家专辑日。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-fatboy-slim-3318190">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ - 胖男孩苗条</a></strong></li></ul><p>此次重新发行是专为国家专辑日重新发行的限量版专辑的独家列表的一部分。今年的活动由 BPI 组织，现已进入第六届，主题围绕 90 年代的大专辑。</p><p>纪念专辑作为一种艺术形式的年度活动已连续第六年，重点关注 90 年代的专辑，为了庆祝，该十年的许多大专辑都将获得特别限量版重新发行。</p><p>这张专辑在 Abbey Road Studios 以半速重新制作，以获得尽可能最佳的音质。 </p><figure id="attachment_3515047" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3515047" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3515047" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press.jpg" alt="Fatboy Slim“宝贝，你已经走过了很长一段路”艺术作品" width="1500" height="1500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fatboy-slim-artwork-press-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515047" class="wp-caption-text"> Fatboy Slim“宝贝，你已经走过了很长一段路”艺术品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>回顾这一具有里程碑意义的周年纪念日，Fatboy Slim 说道：“我仍然对《宝贝，你已经走了很长一段路》的反响感到惊讶和高兴。我没有看到它走向全球，我认为这是一张听起来非常“英国”的唱片。我绝对没有想到 25 年后人们还会谈论它。我记得当时也是这么说的！感谢大家这些年来一直享受它。”</p><p> 《You&#39;ve Come A Long Way, Baby》催生了单曲《Rockafeller Skank》、《Gangster Trippin》、《Praise You》和《Right Here Right Now》，全部进入前十名。制作人获得了全英音乐奖最佳制作人奖以及两项男独唱艺术家和英国单曲奖提名。</p><p> Fatboy Slim 将于 11 月 10 日至 13 日举行的第二届<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-announces-line-up-for-2023-all-back-to-minehead-festival-3428309">All Back to Minehead Festival</a>上亮相。门票现已发售，可<a href="https://www.butlins.com/bigweekenders/weekends/fatboy-slim-presents-all-back-to-minehead/minehead-101123" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到。</p><p> 2023 年的阵容包括 Jodie Harsh、Marshall Jefferson、Mella Dee、Sally C、Saoirse 和 Shanti Celeste。账单上的其他地方还有 Joshua James b2b Bryony Masters、Ell Murphy、Kilimanjaro、Myd 等。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-releases-25th-anniversary-reissue-of-youve-come-a-long-way-baby-for-national-album-day-3515045">Fatboy Slim 为全国专辑日发行 25 周年纪念再版《You&#39;ve Come A Long Way, Baby》，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
